session, and paper presentations on game software engineering topics related to software
engineering education, frameworks for game development and infrastructure, quality
assurance, and model-based game development. The accepted papers are overviewed here.},
booktitle = {Proceedings of the 37th International Conference on Software Engineering - Volume 2},
