/ Pervasive Systems, or Game Development. It addresses technical and methodological
research questions that are typically less well represented in other HCI conferences.
With its focus on engineering interactive systems, the conference has become the premier
venue for all researchers and practitioners interested in the effective and systematic
design and development of innovative, high-quality interactive systems.},
