location, the role of the games as exergames, use in education, and study technical
and safety issues. As a case study, we present O-Mopsi game that combines physical
activity with problem solving. It includes three challenges: (1) navigating to the
next target, (2) deciding the order of targets, (3) physical movement. All of them
