assistive system. This process can be called "gamification". By using motion recognition,
the work processes becomes transparent and can be visualized in real-time. This allows
representing them as bricks in a "production game" which resembles the classic game
Tetris. The aim is to achieve and sustain a mental state called "flow" resulting in
increased motivation and better performance. Although the approach presented here
primarily focuses on elderly and impaired workers, the enhanced assistive system or
