For the second level players needs to respond to random events.In the Network module,
players install and configure network components such as a firewall/router, a WPA2
WIFI, a web filter/proxy, a spam filter and antivirus software. In the Database Module,
players install Apache Web Server, the Data Management System (DBMS) and Database
Applications. Players need to install the database and the web-server in a port different
than their default port, disable default passwords and test for SQL injection before
installing the database. In the Encryption Module, players will be given several scenarios
and need to choose the best encrypting method perform the actions to ensure that the
data is encrypted. The last module integrates content areas from all other modules.},
