scientific data with interaction and game design techniques and 3D computer animation.
Cell Explorer was created through an iterative design process, during which various
tensions related to technical constraints, scientific integrity, aesthetic and user
experience needed to be negotiated. The prototype is an educational tool that offers
users a unique experience to facilitate a more meaningful engagement with scientific
