meaning (language) and significance (semiology) of Kashgar heritage. In practice,
this research promotes the acceptance of content-based analysis for designing a system
of alternate realities with contribution on the multidisciplinary field of digital
heritage that combines interactive online media, architectural cultural heritage and
game datamining.},
